  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                             New Update!  DECEMBER 2025 - SCALLYWAG SPLASHDOWN is now OPEN!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/e458996520d8a23498416d5ae89cd80a.avif?t=1766804688\" width=400 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into the eerie world of **Escape from Toon Kingdom**—keep it in your Wishlist and stay tuned as updates bring fresh challenges, haunting atmospheres, and twisted surprises.</strong><br> <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/8c11a13771ae05dc6cda6b6b1e8baf14.poster.avif?t=1766804688\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/8c11a13771ae05dc6cda6b6b1e8baf14.webm?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/8c11a13771ae05dc6cda6b6b1e8baf14.mp4?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape From Toon Kingdom</strong> is a 1–4 player co-op horror game. Play as mascots trapped in a dying theme park. Explore. Solve. Suffer. Every attraction holds a secret—and a piece of your escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/1c35418f0636cc5679ff0f9d074cbfe9.avif?t=1766804688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras_big/1c35418f0636cc5679ff0f9d074cbfe9.avif?t=1766804688 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/b3ec2e494202aa96a5f5102aa7d2cd33.poster.avif?t=1766804688\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/b3ec2e494202aa96a5f5102aa7d2cd33.webm?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/b3ec2e494202aa96a5f5102aa7d2cd33.mp4?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as one of the park’s mascots, now fighting for survival. Work together with up to 4 players in this co-op adventure, or brave the terror alone in single-player mode. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/3152f05dafa252654bfa24e50ac29963.avif?t=1766804688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras_big/3152f05dafa252654bfa24e50ac29963.avif?t=1766804688 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/2173b6adf997dfaab73a02c40bb1bbab.poster.avif?t=1766804688\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/2173b6adf997dfaab73a02c40bb1bbab.webm?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/2173b6adf997dfaab73a02c40bb1bbab.mp4?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse twisted versions of the park's once-cheerful attractions, each filled with sinister traps, deformed creatures, and spine-chilling surprises.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/1766052095c5f5a72e97d61c705be869.avif?t=1766804688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras_big/1766052095c5f5a72e97d61c705be869.avif?t=1766804688 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to face the horrors and break free from the park's grasp? The attractions have come alive, and terror awaits around every corner. <strong>Escape from Toon Kingdom</strong>—where nightmares take center stage! </p>",
